{"questionId":"6bfd0c2e-65a8-46f9-a800-10203b4c8d45_10","correctAnswer":"8","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Multiply the expressions","content":"Combine like terms: $$7x^6+9x^6-8x^6=(7+9-8)x^6=8x^6.$$"},{"title":"Identify b","content":"Comparing $8x^6=bx^6$ gives $b=8$. The answer is <strong>8</strong>."}]}